    "text": [
        "Dear Ali,",
        "I hope this letter finds you well. I have missed your birthday party, so I am writing to apologise and explain why I could not come.",
        "Unfortunately, I did not attend your party and I am very sorry about this matter. In fact, I was planning for that from last week and I was very happy to see you and our friends.",
        "I have s strong reason for my absence. Indeed, in the evening of your party's day, my mother had called me and asked me to go to the hospital. Thus, I went there immediately and found my father had an terrible car accident and his leg was broken. Therefore, I was at hospital until midnight.",
        "Finally, I like to see you and celebrate your party. If you are free on Saturday, we can go to the Italian restaurant that is near the shopping mall.",
        "Do write back soom. I am longing to see you.",
        "Lots of love,",
        "Mohammad"
    ],
